 can't invis be like SoW and last a given amount of time.  I'm about tired of dying because I get the 'You appear' message on my way through a dangerous area.  Nothing like losing 2 days worth of xp in 20 seconds.  One death due to a bad pull, one due to You appear on my way back to my corpse.  Makes me sick.<br>
<br>
Nurpus<br>
