Terris Thule <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> Pota</span><br> <span class=usertitle>Unregistered User</span><br>   <font color=#333333>(10/14/00 5:30:10 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerrants.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=38.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   I agree</span><hr size=1> Relatively my only complaint about my mage is the innate ability for invisibility spells to fade in 5 seconds. Now at lvl 36, that is just unacceptable. Does anyone know if Verant has ever addressed this? I once asked a fellow mage if he hates that, and he said , &quot;Just max your Divination out..&quot; . This does not make any difference.. my Divination is always maxed, and specialization is maxed out also. Just a strange phenomena for us mages I guess..<br>
<br>
Pota Shmota lvl 36 Magi on Prexus server <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> HEY</span><br> <span class=usertitle>Unregistered User</span><br>   <font color=#333333>(10/16/00 4:33:49 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerrants.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=38.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   YEAH!</span><hr size=1> Worst spot is Kithacor forest.....baaaaaad stuff in there, or in a kos city.<br>
